title: Get Out of Your Head
description:
Sadie welcomes bible teacher, author, and founder, of the IF:GATHERING, Jennie Allen, to the podcast. Listen in as they discuss Jennie’s latest book, Get Out of Your Head, as well as share advice on mentorship, authenticity, and overcoming toxic thoughts.
